main_body:
The production levies in the sugar sector shall be as follows for the 2002/03 marketing year:
(a) EUR 12,638 per tonne of white sugar as the basic production levy on A sugar and B sugar;
(b) EUR 126,139 per tonne of white sugar as the B levy on B sugar;
(c) EUR 5,330 per tonne of dry matter as the basic production levy on A isoglucose and B isoglucose;
(d) EUR 55,093 per tonne of dry matter as the B levy on B isoglucose;
(e) EUR 12,638 per tonne of dry matter equivalent sugar/isoglucose as the basic production levy on A inulin syrup and B inulin syrup;
(f) EUR 126,139 per tonne of dry matter equivalent sugar/isoglucose as the B levy on B inulin syrup.
